comments: This was a difficult class - but passed with great teacher assistance

Great sense of humor, and absolutely adorable. Her english is broken, and she has a thick accent, but will slow down or repeat things for clarity if you ask. I had her for labs only, but she was very helpful with any question you brought to her

Had her for lab only, VERY hard to understand but an easy A for sure. She is willing to help and is an adorable woman, it\'s just hard to get the help you need sometimes because of the language barrier.
she is so adorable i love her outfits every week. she always helped when i asked for it
she does have a very strong accent..but shes so cute and adorable! she answers every single question i ask her..i like her a lot
Very hard to understand, from Russia, heavy accent, but very nice lady! Teaches Chemistry and also teaches the Chemistry labs.
